des:
Thanks to this skill you will be able to hear the laugh of Joker, the disturbing and intriguing character in the masterpiece played by Joaquin Phoenix.
Acclaimed by the critics and at the top of the box office rankings.
Discover the Joker's laugh, a harrowing and suffocating, disquieting and paradoxical laugh.
